{"tha-ap528:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap528:0.2":"Tinadayakavagga ","tha-ap528:0.3":"Dandadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap528:1.1":"“Kananam vanamogayha, ","tha-ap528:1.2":"velum chetvanaham tada; ","tha-ap528:1.3":"Alambanam karitvana, ","tha-ap528:1.4":"sanghassa adadim bahum. ","tha-ap528:2.1":"Tena cittappasadena, ","tha-ap528:2.2":"subbate abhivadiya; ","tha-ap528:2.3":"Alambadandam datvana, ","tha-ap528:2.4":"pakkamim uttaramukho. ","tha-ap528:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap528:3.2":"yam dandamadadim tada; ","tha-ap528:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap528:3.4":"dandadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap528:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap528:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap528:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap528:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap528:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap528:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap528:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap528:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap528:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap528:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma dandadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap528:8.1":"Dandadayakattherassapadanam chattham. ","tha-ap528:8.2":"Tevisatimam bhanavaram. "}